info.description: What ===== Pythonic ZoneMinder wrapper - API - Event Server - Logger - Memory - Machine Learning Modules Documentation & Examples ========================= Latest documentation is available here. The documentation includes a full example. Features ========= - API auth using tokens or legacy (manages refresh logins automatically) - Monitors - Events with filters - States - Configs - EventNotification callbacks - Mapped Memory access - Direct access to ML algorithms - [Amazon Rekognition support](https://medium.com/@michael-ludvig/aws-rekognition-support-for-zoneminder-object-detection-40b71f926a80) for object detection Limitations ============ * Only for Python3
info.name: pyzm
info.summary: ZoneMinder API, Logger and other base utilities for python programmers
